snippet.title: Conqueror's Blade - Season VI: Scourge of Winter (Release Trailer)
snippet.description: Terror holds the land in its icy clutches. Rise up, resist, and take back the North in Season VI: Scourge of Winter, now available in Conqueror's Blade as a free update! Read more: https://conqblade.com/news/662
